data.description: Welcome home!!!, Beautiful 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms Single Family Residence located at Reedy Reserve community. This property offers indoor laundry. Community pool. Conveniently located near Highway 192, shopping & restaurants. Open floor plan with amazing lighting and tile flooring in the kitchen and bathrooms. Granite counters and spacious pantry.  Dual Sinks in both Bathrooms. Stainless steel Refrigerator.  Ring camera doorbell, security cameras, security coded lock set in front door. Solar System. Investors welcome on this great investment opportunity! Schedule your private tour today!
